Imam Khomeini Spaceport
پایانه فضایی امام خمینی
General information
Status Complete
Location southeast Semnan, Iran
Coordinates 35°14′16.8″N 53°57′02.8″E﻿ / ﻿35.238000°N 53.950778°E﻿ / 35.238000; 53.950778
Opened July 27, 2017; 13 months ago (2017-07-27)[1]

Imam Khomeini Spaceport (Persian:پایانه فضایی امام خمینی) is an Iranian space vehicle launch facility (spaceport) located in the Semnan,[2] and it is part of Semnan Space Center.

Simorgh Launch Pad at Imam Khomeini Space Center
Launch Corridor of the Imam Khomeini Space Center
